social_posts.post_text: Stay Tuned hit a MILLION Views! Our cheap turbo Lincoln ep just cleared 1MM views on YT. We are having a blast over here. Making the move to YouTube and Hagerty has been awesome. Love working with this small but killer team. @mbarbalinardo @thakingofhearts @therealslimzimmy are all champions. Click the profile link if you want to catch up!
Wheels UP! Throwing the @qa1motorsports drag package at my ‘74 Firebird. Their new stuff is SO nice. Blower this week. Wheelies soon! #hangemhigh
Took the Cheap Turbo Lincoln to @maplegrove1320 and let that thing EAT! Scroll to pic 2 for the results! Episode is up now. #oopsididitagain

“We’re Gonna Lose The Shop” shirts are back!!! These sold out QUICK last time so grab them while they are still around! Our fulfillment guys will do their best to get em out ASAP! Click the link in my profile to grab one! These are hand printed in Philadelphia at @awesome_dudes_printing.

Got an random email from a guy telling me to come scoop his Dad’s 1975 Electra with a 455 built by Motion Performance. It had been sitting in a garage in Spanish Harlem for nearly 20 years. We went out there, got it running, drove it all the way back to Old Bridge New Jersey, and then had an absolute blast in it! Car is an animal and it was such a fun time. New episode Monday.

Got an email from a dude who said his Dad’s 73 Electra with NOS and a hot 455 was wasting away in an NYC garage, and did I want it?! So we went up there, got it running, limped it back to Etown, and got it working right and it’s a RIPPER!! Ep is up on the Hagerty YT!  Link is in my profile. Really stoked on this one, was a blast.

Electric HORSEPOWER!? Just scooped this deeply trashed Tesla P90D! The plan is to take the battery and drive unit out of this dorkmobile and jam it into something cool! I can’t argue with all this power, I want to see what it’s all about! Plans for the swap: 1)don’t ruin an iconic hot-rod 2)keep it simple, and as low bucks as possible 3)make sure it hauls ass when we are done!! I’m super pumped to get cracking. I’m not coming for your gas cars, I’m not going to turn you into a vegetarian, I won’t make you get a man-bun, I’m just trying to have some fun!

Finally found those Horses!! After getting that @speedmaster1979 6-71 bolted to my @butlerperformance 462 stroker motor, this thing came alive! It made 335WHP on this dyno NA, what does it make now at 7psi?! Closest guess gets a holiday cheer Stay Tuned Gear package!!

The King is gone. Rest In Peace, Ken Block. An absolute icon, pioneer and someone I admired a great deal. They say we stand on the shoulders of giants, none bigger than this guy. My deepest condolences to his family, and the @thehoonigans gang. Godspeed.

Finally HORSEPOWERS!! After roasting the tires on the dyno first run at @psrperformance, this thing did 569 HP at the tires! I’ll dig back through my old post and find a winner for Stay Tuned gear! @davidfreiburger guessed 569 first, but he already got a Stay Tuned gear set. Can’t wait for this episode to come out. 569HP/608tq at about 7psi on this @butlerperformance 462 with the @speedmaster1979 blower. That’s going to be our @sickthemag Sick Week setup, hoping to crack into the 10’s at least once in sunny Florida.

Want this sweet @wirecare_inc shirt FOR FREE?! Here’s how: go on their website through my link and buy 25 bucks worth of wire, zip ties, tools, connectors or any other great stuff they carry and get this shirt FREE!! Link is www.wirecare.com/tar Stoked to work with this rad NJ company on a bunch of upcoming builds. Go out and gear up! Firebird episode with the blower drops next week and I can’t wait for y’all to see it.

Back on my bullshit. Drift car stuff is moving forward. Swapping my rust bucket ‘90 240sx for a RUST-FREE, caged, wide body hatch. SR20 is going into this thing to make the drift chariot of my 2005 dreams! Let’s GOOOO

Old-School blowers are unbeatable! Big power, bigger attitude! My ‘74 Street Freak Firebird came alive when we bolted this @speedmaster1979 onto the @butlerperformance 462 stroker!! Ep comes out Monday on @hagerty YT. We have worked so hard on this thing and it’s turning out killer. #staytuned #winwithholley

Drift Boys are back in town. I had an incredible week throwing together this Nissan 240sx with the SR20 from my rusty coupe. @eagleeyeedwards came down and once we turned the Judas Priest up on the radio and started working past 11pm, it felt like 2003 all over again. This thing hits the dyno next week, and I can’t wait for sideways spring time (after A LOT MORE work). Really feeling thankful to work with such a great team that’s up for anything.

8 years ago today, I went to the HRG garage to interview with a producer and @davidfreiburger about a job, and posted this killer ‘55 Chevy I was seeing for the first time. What a wild ride that turned out to be

Smoke ‘em, if you’ve got ‘em! This ‘Bird is BACK. Once we bolted this blower on, I swear my mustache became thicker, and the sleeves blew off my shirt. It’s a full-on 80’s masterpiece again. Full video is up now on YT. Click the link in my profile. #staytuned #letsparty

See you at Race Wars @finnegan999 ! Just blew the cobwebs out of this SR20DET that’s been sitting for a decade and it’s a BEAST. @jimmyoakes playing keyboards on this @link_ecu setup and it sounds bananas. Turn it up and hear them turbo sounds! #boostisbest #letsparty
Whatever works right?? We even replaced the piece we chopped out, like real professionals!
Wheels Up starter kit: Big slicks, @quick_performance 9inch with @speedmaster1979 guts, an old NASCAR T101 4speed, and popping the clutch at 5500 RPM. See y’all at @sickthemag Week!

She’s a Runner! @eagleeyeedwards scooped this ‘87 Ramcharger that’s been frozen in one spot since ‘02. It doesn’t roll, and was dropped off a flatbed (aggressively), but it runs! 360 LA motor cracked right off with some shots of @gumout and one the belt broke off of the stick air pump it ran mega smooth. I actually took a day off this week to see his new place and meet his new baby, which was amazing, but of course we wound up messing around with cars at one point.

When your crusty SR20DET hits WAY TOO HARD on the first run on the dyno! @jimmyoakes let ‘er rip at 17psi in 5th gear and I was waiting for pistons to land in the ceiling @psrperformance . He brought it back to earth and everything left in one piece! Full episode is on the Hagerty YT now. Link is in my profile.
We do sleep training a little differently over here. Making sure @mbarbalinardo is ready to sleep on the road at @sickthemag week ‘23! #sleeptraining #letsparty #sickweek

Things got a little spicy on the first serious burnout with my ‘74 Firebird. Slipped the clutch until it welded everything into one. My Bad on this one! I think there’s a hashtag or something about this kind of happening.

Sick Week or BUST!!! After a serious push this week, the Stay Tuned gang (and a couple special guests) got a ton of major last minute needs handled on the Street Freak Firebird. Going bumperless in the back with a sweet tow hitch/bash bar with some drift car vibes. (Not sold on silver, may change). This has been SO MUCH work
for our team but everyone killed it.  It’s one thing to make a car run for a few minutes of footage, an entirely different story to drive and race it across the south. This car hasn’t seen much action since the 90’s. Hoping to finish Sick Week, and everything else is gravy. Trying to dial a name in for this thing. Feeling Head Poncho but open to
suggestions. @sickthemag #winwithholley #letsparty #headponcho

I was told to do a “Big Burnout” to get these new @mickeythompsontires slicks up to temp. Apparently this was “excessive”? I learn more drag racing stuff every day! Sick Week kicks off tomorrow! A couple killer shake down runs and I’m extremely stoked. We’re put in so much work on this thing and the response has been awesome. #headponcho #winwithholley #sickweek2023

Sick Week is Now!!! I’m rolling in my Firebird with @therealslimzimmy this week. Goals are : 1) actually finish the event 2)average 11.99 or better for the week and 3) turn it up until we run a 10.99 or better on Friday. Can we do it? We’ve already smoked a fuel pump, missed a few turns and ran out of gas (all before the first checkpoint). @sickthemag #letsparty #headponcho

Wheels up! Leaving the line at Bradenton with a sliver of daylight under both tires. Ran 11.8 at 120 yesterday spinning through first gear, and ran 11.9 today at 105. Car is falling on its face after 2nd gear. We killed a fuel pump (our fault), and have been chasing problems since. Metal bits all downstream mean we are going through the carbs again. It’s a 300 mile street drive and C group runs first tomorrow. Looking like it’s gonna be a long night, but that’s the fun of it, I think. Goal of averaging 11.99 or better is still alive! #sickweek2023

When your car isn’t running right, you don’t want to find problems, but you don’t not want to find problems either. Collapsed pushrod in cyl 1 on our 462 Pontiac @butlerperformance motor, this thing happily motored 300 miles like this up to GA, parking lot engine work happening, now. Trying to make the last “all run” session, since C group is up first today. #sickweek2023

Cracked off a 12.1 during the last session of the day after scrambling all morning!  Still nosing over but time, but our goal of 11.99 or better average is alive, swipe for my happy face. Heading to @ksrperformancefabrication to get it on the dyno for some sorting!

Just left @ksrperformancefabrication making EVERY SINGLE HORSEPOWERS it should! We are back in business for #sickweek2023! I can’t wait to send this thing tomorrow! Huge thanks to Kevin at KSR for getting us sorted out.
#headponcho #letsparty

Knocking’ on TENS!!! Best pass ever by a ton!  11.0 at 124 MPH, and it feels awesome! Best launch ever, doing my best to figure out this stick shift drag racing thing. I was so pumped on the return road! Disregard the other time on the slip, some girl in ‘55 was HAULING ASS. #winwithholley
It’s Party Pulley time!!! Last day of @sickthemag week and we are hunting for a 10 second pass! Best so far is 11.06 and hoping to find a little more speed today! LET’S GO!

We finished Sick Week and I DIDN’T BREAK IT!! Came in with no testing and a car that had only a could hundred miles on it since the 90’s and made it all the way through! We averaged 11.60 for the week, ran 11.0 the last two days and actually finished 6th in the stick shift class! Launching a 3900 lb stick car is not easy, and I can’t wait to get that dialed. Extremely stoked to be able to keep it together and keep chasing a 10 second pass back in PA! @therealslimzimmy was a killer co-pilot, and @thakingofhearts was shooting everything for an upcoming Stay Tuned Ep! Photo by the one and only @keithturk200

We’ve got HOODIES NOW! Stay Tuned Logo and “Angelo’s Gym”
are live in the merch store just in time for more gross NE weather! Link is in my profile! Been working on a bunch of new designs, so #staytuned! (Yes, there’s a Firebird shirt coming)

Sick Week Episode is up now! It’s a ONE HOUR EPIC following our adventures all over Florida. We broke down, fixed the car, went fast; went slow, ran out of gas, saw so many rad cars and parking lots, and chased fast times. Incredible work by @thakingofhearts to capture it all singlehanded. Kick back and check it out! Link is in my profile and story!

Another one bites the dust! Looks like things got pretty real when our cheap turbo Lincoln hit the strip! Lmk if anyone has a built short block near Philly! Trying to get this thing back in action. 4v 4.6 Ford Engine from our '98 Mark Viii. #oops

Keep track of all your pistons, you don’t want to lose any. This little guy tried to escape at the 1000ft mark last track day. Our Lincoln will live again, but this block won’t. Go ahead, use the hashtag.

Happy International Women’s Day! Dedicating this one to my Momma. She got two advanced degrees while being a full time Mom to four maniacs and went on to a very esteemed career in local higher education. I’ve been doing a little water pump repair on her Lexus the last couple of days, and tried to wind up my parents with a text of the @on3performance turbo sitting in the bay, but it seems like Mom was ready to rock. We’re gonna have to boost this thing up next time. #letsparty

New Sticker sheets and “Lose The Shop” slappers are HERE! We’ve got the fastest fridge in town. Upgrade your helmets, tools boxes, fridges, kids faces, laptops, whatever! Designed by @happarabbit and SO rad. Click the link in my profile to order and I appreciate the support a ton!
Still tastes like a piston. Or chicken, or something. We dug deep into our Cheap Turbo Lincoln looking to revive this thing. Full video on Stay Tuned today.

Lucky Number 7! Just scooped up my SEVENTH 2nd gen Rx-7 and it’s basically a carbon copy of my very first one. 19 year old me saved my pennies and grabbed a white turbo 2 to drive while my Demon was apart and I got absolutely hooked on sliding it around. This car legitimately changed my life. I haven’t had a rotary powered car in at least 10 years and I’m ready to be hurt again. Looking for a complete t2 drivetrain now, and resisting the urge to cram it full of freedom (had an SBC w/6-71 at some point) so if you have any leads lmk. #staytuned #initiald #letsparty

SBC or 13B??? This FC turned out quite a bit rattier than expected, no chassis wiring, NA weak rear end, no HVAC, some rust, roof half caved in but it’s still got me deep in the feels. It has SBC mounts and could be up and ripping in no time, or I can spend the time and start collecting half of an RX-7 to put this thing back together and get to building a beast rotary engine and have the car I really want at some point. What’s the play??

Rough and ROWDY. Whipped this SBC together from stuff we had laying around and one big @summitracing order and this car is a ROCKET!! Full video is out today! We aren’t nearly done with rotary dreams, moving forward on that quickly too, just in a new and more serious direction. This was a wild week, this crew is awesome. #letsparty

Firebird Shirts are here!! We went full 70’s with these and they came out so rad. Proper 3/4 sleeve baseball shirts featuring my Street Freak Firebird on the front with the back done up with the entire Sick Week ‘23 tour on the back. Likely only doing one run of these so grab ‘em while you can! Click the link in my profile to grab one. @happarabbit crushed the design on these things! Printed with pride in PA by @awesome_dudes_printing

WE DID IT! Broke into the 10’s!! In full street trim, at 3900lbs with iron stock heads (ported) and full old school tech! Ran 10.81 at 128, my Street Freak Firebird is a bonafide 10 second car. It will all be out in very special episode on YouTube soon! #letsparty

Blastin’ Freedom straight out of the tailpipes! A big iron supercharged V8, topped with 2 sideways carburetors, a dog box 4 speed, and enough sparkle to see from space. Every time I hit the 2-step a bald eagle gets pregnant, I know it. I love this thing.

Cheap Turbo Lincoln is coming back with a vengeance! We scooped up a fully forged stroker 4.6 with cams and ARP everything on the cheap! Happy 4/6 day to all who celebrate. Yes, I washed and combed my hair, don’t make it weird.

Happy Birthday to my guy @mbarbalinardo ! Dude is the reason we get anything done at Stay Tuned. He keeps the whole party rolling and probably doesn’t get the credit he deserves! Anyway, some big stuff coming soon and we couldn’t do it without ole Barb.

600 HP Lincoln INCOMING! About to push 20PSI through this fully built 4.6 and make a name for Grandpa cars everywhere. I love this thing. @holleyperformance running the tune and @gearstarpro turning that power into tire smoke.

Making my favorite kind of sandwich. This beast @manticclutchusa custom twin-plate clutch for my Pontiac 462 in the Street Freak Firebird! This thing can take all 700ish crank HP it’s pumping out and then some. It’ll be featured in the next episode on the car, and it’s a sweet piece of kit. #headponcho #letsparty Hand modeling by @mbarbalinardo  #staytuned
No Pain, No Gain! Sick Week Prep/Chasing 10’s episode drops tomorrow. It’s my favorite video in a while! Epic 80’s montage, scored by the one and only @boyjohnny #letsparty

Big NEWS! All New Stay Tuned Episodes will air on MY YouTube channel! We are super pumped to be able to be back to our rowdy selves. First full length episode goes live tonight at 5! Covers the Firebird and chasing 10’s at the track! There’s gonna be a weekly video, but putting up two this week to get rolling! Really excited and mildly terrified to go out on our own, LET’S GO! Speaking with other YouTubers and sponsors helped us make the decision. We did a stint on a larger, more corporate channel and it wasn’t a great fit, thankful to Hagerty for the opportunity, and no regrets at all.

I have ALWAYS wanted a Syclone. This was the quickest vehicle in the world in ‘91 and the fastest truck to 60 FOR THIRTY YEARS. I went to buy the cheapest running and driving (roughly) one I could find in 2000 miles. Full vid up on ST tomorrow! Any guesses on the asking price in todays market??

Did I spend FIFTEEN THOUSAND American dollars on a 100k Syclone that had seen a fire, needed everything, and kept throwing the worlds first check engine light just trying to idle? Hell no I didn’t! Introducing the “Sike-Clone”! A $1200 rust free ‘88 S10 that we are going to turn into a homegrown AWD turbo monster! As much as I love the Syclones I’m not a collector and I actually wouldn’t feel great modifying one heavily. FULL Ep is up on the Stay Tuned YT NOW! (Full credit to @patrick.devlin.art for the name!)

Grandpa’s Lincoln is BACK UP! Just fired up our cheap turbo Mark VIII with new fully forged stroker 4.6 4V and this thing revs like a dirt bike! Full Ep will be on Stay Tuned FRIDAY!This was a TON of work but so much fun and this car turned out so nasty. #letsparty #letspizza #staytuned

We’re Back Up! If you see some Grandpa’s Mark Viii running around SE PA on CR Kai reps, and sounding like the blower motor on a bounce house, maybe let it be! This thing is packing some HEAT. Full Ep is on the Stay Tuned YT channel tonight at 5pm!

Hot Rodders since 1956 “throw a small block in it!” And it RULES EVERY SINGLE TIME. This little RX-7 got some track-tuned upgrades and it’s going to be a riot. Full ep this Friday. You can't see @therealslimzimmy face but he LOVES this thing.
This V8 Rx-7 can get up to about 47MPH in about 12 parking spaces if you try hard enough. Full Ep on Stay Tuned YT!
Blew the welds right off that puppy. I guess we forgot to rub the snake.

ELECTRIC MUSCLE Day 1! Tearing down our P90D that has met an immovable object with some serious speed. 762 Electric Horsepowers made this the quickest sedan ever in 2015. Question: does anyone know how to break into a Tesla?

Dorman Ls2 Intake Giveaway! Win this sweet cathedral port LSx intake! Plus Stay Tuned shirts and stickers. All you have to do to enter is: Like this post! Follow @dormanproducts and follow me (prob already doing that). Stoked on this giveaway package, don’t miss this one, it will fit just about any cathedral port LS setup, and they flow really well! Full rules are in the link in my profile!
Lincoln Dyno Session will be up on Stay Tuned tonight! A LOT of ups and downs with the new forged motor and trying to get it all dialed! Grab a brew and see what it do.

PENDING: 2000 Ford F-250 6.8L V10 2WD. CA truck I bought in 2016, and hauled to PA with it. Absolutely zero rust on it (one of one in PA). 145 K miles, in very solid shape. A ton of maintenance done in the last few years. Just towed to FL and back. Unloading it to get something diesel powered since we are going to be making long hauls more. Looking for 8k and I don’t think you’ll find a cleaner body anywhere in the Northeast! Upgraded with Banks Power: headers, exhaust, TB, intake Replaced in the last two years: plugs, coils, balljoints, suspension bushings, shocks, fuel pump, pads, rotors, tires, etc. 
EMAIL ME: tangelocarsales@gmail.com
Gotta know what to look for.
Swipe for bad ideas. Super fun vid is on Stay Tuned now with this v8 swapped FC. Link is in my profile.
Guess Who’s Back?? #2jznoshit #treadcarefully

CD009 6speed with a Collins 2JZ adapter, and Tipton twin plate going in place of that slush box. Stoked to rip around with 3 pedals, and see if there’s any tire left before handing back over to @thakingofhearts
Tore apart this Tesla and didn’t even explode myself! First Vid is up on the tubes now! Get in these comments and start hollering! Link is in my profile!

You guys ever have a couple and then throw a lowball bid of $6900 on a clean 996 in the middle of the night on @ebaymotors because you think it’s funny, and then wake up and you accidentally bought the cheapest 911 in forever?!!
Mercedes 2JZ swap just got so much cooler with a 6 speed manual swap! Full story is up on the tubes at 5!

I’ve never dunked on a regulation hoop but I know it can’t feel any better than this did. Quick front seal job on the 2JZ Merc so we can hit the dyno tomorrow. Credit to @mbarbalinardo for the GUUHHH sounds. #2jz
Top down, boost up. After much failure the 2JZ Benz is RIPPING up these PA streets. Closed course, professional idiot. New vid tomorrow on Stay Tuned!

Big Riggin’ to Chi-town in my new ‘04 Ram 2500! I’ve had great luck towing long hauls with these common-rail Cummins and at 218k this thing is just getting broken in. It came with this snorkel hood, ridiculous wheels and a few cans of Krylon mods on stock parts. Just tossed on a set of @mickeythompsontires Classic III wheels wrapped in @falkentire Wildpeak R/T01 33’s and we are going to scoop up the 911 I bought on @ebaymotors! Stoked.

We’re bringing our Merch fulfillment in-house! We know there have been issues with shipping and our staff here will be handling all shipping, logistics and anything else! ALSO: All shirts are now silkscreen printed in PA by @pinkbikeralph or @awesome_dudes_printing ! We’ve just got a ton of stock in all sizes so order up or we just might LOSE THE SHOP! Link is in my profile!
Take one dirt cheap 911, add one junkyard 5.3LS full of freedom ponies, and let’s party! Building the grimiest, fastest Porsche around, first video is up Friday.
“Siri, play Thin Lizzy.” #blasphemi #theboysarebackintown

I’m running my Firebird at @race4thehouse at @maplegrove1320 on June 17th! Get out there, watch some racing, grab a t-shirt and support a really cool charity the Children’s Hospital of Philly. See y’all there

Came down to NC to put in some time with my guy @finnegan999 and some of his bros to do some upgrades on #blasphemi and actually spend some time on testing and tuning before the next drag and drive we do. Oh and get behind the wheel of this beast myself for some passes! It was immediately like old times! Nothing fit, scrambling for parts and plans, I was lifting a transmission in the first five minutes and we had some big struggles and bigger laughs! It will all unfold on the Stay Tuned channel next week, so uh Stay Tuned! #sleeptime

I stopped by @chavisperformanceengineering to put the screws to these 2 911s (hard life, I know). Left car is powered by an Ls3 GM 495Hp v8 installed with all Chavis parts, on the right a 911 Turbo from Porsche. The left car was absolutely more fun to drive, tractable, killer powerband and everything worked! Full vid is on the U tubes now (link in profile). Picked up everything I’ll need to build my own RWD LS 911 and I can’t wait to get rolling.

With my oldest (7) getting the Street Freak firebird ready for @race4thehouse this weekend! She called it the “Fire Hawk” and “The Phoenix”, and I like both of those names! Waiting on repainted bumpers and filler panels from @crollscustoms and it should be good to go!
Just scooped an AWD Astro van for under a grand, and I’m SO EXCITED. Who knows what this means??? #anotherdayanotherslay

Epic week with @finnegan999 and #blasphemi last week. We fought with this thing tooth and nail all week and had a blast the whole time. Some friends when you see ‘em you pick right up where you left off. Full vid up on the ST tube at 5PM!

Gorgeous day here @maplegrove1320 for @race4thehouse event! I’m here running the ‘Bird! We’re selling ST merch in the pits and all proceeds are going to the Race 4The House charity that goes to the Children’s Hospital of Philadelphia.

Before I can cram a cranked up 5.3 into the back of my 911, I need to sort out the transmission! I’ve got the G96 6speed from my original ‘99 convertible. It would pop out of first and second gear in those synchros are definitely shot. I need someone to refresh this box and install my @wavetrac_differentials , closer to PA the better. I can’t order my clutch or the LSD until I find someone to do it up so let me know!
The first day of summer has the temps WAY up, and if your car’s fan can’t keep up, get yourself down to @advanceautoparts and grab a new cooling fan from @dormanproducts OEM Solutions line.

Gene is the man. He’s the guy that built, painted and owned my Street Freak Firebird in ‘83! We got to reunite him with his old ‘Bird, show him all the work that we’ve done to it, and even got him behind the wheel for a rip! It was an amazing time. It’s all up on Stay Tuned at quitting time today!

Man, this one got me right in the feels. The answer just straight HUSTLE! Just 4 individuals cranking away building Stay Tuned and generally having a blast. Feedback has been killer, and really appreciate all the support!

Sketch Level: MIDNIGHT. Rescuing @brenden_jones 1978 Ford Camper body swap on a ‘97 Ram 3500 chassis today. We built this beast forever ago and it’s a machine. He left it on a farm three years ago and it deserves a new go at the highways. Brenden doesn’t know how to store a vehicle but man he can wear a pair of pants.
FINALLY! Fishtail ‘Cuda is back! My Drift/Street 6.4 Hemi powered project got dragged out of the barn this week and turned into the sweet handling car I always wanted! Ep is up on Stay Tuned tonight!
House of Horrors in the shop today. About to start selling tickets to spectators, eat a slice and watch us cheat death!

The new @qa1motorsports Mopar front suspension is KILLER. Out of the box performance doesn’t really get any better! My ‘Cuda steers and handles like I always hoped it would! Track days soon! #letsparty #staytuned

location.city_name: Land of the Free Home of the Brave

social_posts.post_text: Advanced Hot Dog Eating! On this 4th of July, enjoy your Freedom and get yourself a dog, split down the middle and cram a pickle spear in there. Every bite is a a 10/10! Enjoy the day. Happy Birthday America!

There’s a racer in one of these girls,  I know it! Being a girl Dad absolutely rules, and I haven’t really been pushing cars and racing on them, hoping they come to it naturally. They are getting old enough to be involved more and that’s super exciting. My twins are going to be 5 later in the year. Ceci is nearly 3 years past her liver transplant and doing really well, and she’s totally fearless so she might just be the one.

Truck Resurrected! We dragged this very special ‘78 F250 out of the weeds last week and got it back on the road. It’s @brenden_jones truck. We built it nearly a decade ago and it’s a sweet old Ford body sitting on a ‘97 Ram 3500 Cummins 5 speed frame. It’s an absolute UNIT. Full story on Stay Tuned tomorrow!
Stay Alert, Stay Alive. Looked safe from my end on this run but @thakingofhearts might feel different. #staytuned
How it started/How it’s going. Sike Clone time! Going turbo/AWD in our cheap S10! Y’all going turbo LS, SBC, or just boost up the 4.3 that came in the Astro?
The ‘Barb doesn’t fall far from the tree! @mbarbalinardo Pop came down in his ‘55 today. LS procharged 6.0, one piece glass front end. I can attest that it makes the JAM.

Blowing the cobwebs off my Street Freak ‘Bird today! Catch me and the ‘Bird at @syracusenationals this weekend! I’ll be up there Saturday and I can’t wait to check out this LEGENDARY show. We will be out front whipping together a 6.0 parking lot style for @mbarbalinardo car! Should be a killer time. Come get a high five and turn some wrenches! Bringing up some limited Stay Tuned merch too!
Junkyard 4.3 + cheap turbo kit for the AWD SikeClone!! I’m ready to learn the hard way (again). Can we build a faster, cheaper, better Syclone?  Full ep will be on Stay Tuned tonight!

Landed at @syracusenationals! I’ll be thrashing a junkyard 6.0 LS together with @mbarbalinardo today at our Stay Tuned booth. We are bunked in with @tuccihotrods ! Come grab a high five and a shirt, we’ve got a limited supply of merch!
A guy delivered the coolest custom @hotwheelsofficial he made of our V8 FC, and he even put PIZZA on it! So cool, I will hang it right up in the shop. Thanks @alexl_a1 #staytuned4ever

New foam will get you home! Just redid the drivers seat in my ‘04 Ram (220k): fixed some slipped springs, new beefy foam and a fresh cover. Best 200 bucks and an hour I’ve spent in a long while. If you have a car build in the last 25 years (one of these modern jobs)  they usually don’t use hog rings and it’s a simple procedure. I get HYPED about the most random things and I probably talked about this seat halfway to the @syracusenationals .

Boost Timing Reduction for zero dollars! I figured out how to convert a vacuum advance unit from any run of the mill distributor into a turbo ready unit. -pull off the vacuum diaphragm -pry the crimp apart -swap the spring seat to the other side of the arm - cut spring in half (so you don’t get spring bind) -install spring on the arm side of the diaphragm -crimp back together and reinstall! Tested out great! Not quite as much travel as before but I guess it will pull 8* or so! I’m going to test it with a timing light and simulated 10psi as soon as this SikeClone fires up!
